               <t:birth when="1695"/>
               <t:age>He was 21 years of age when he became a king</t:age>
               <t:floruit notBefore="1716" notAfter="1721">He succeeded his brother King <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9152TaklaHa">Takla Hāymānot I</t:persName> in <t:date> 1716</t:date>.
